  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a randomized controlled trial whose purpose is to evaluate the efficacy of therapy
      with lactulose and rifaximin associated with a vegetable diet in the prevention of post-TIPS
      hepatic encephalopathy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
